Senior Analyst/Analyst
06 May 2014 12:14 AM - UAE
Senior Analyst/Analyst required for a private investment company managing a global multi-asset class portfolio.Key responsibilities are: Assist in the analysis of potential investment opportunities across all asset classes (including listed equity, public fixed income, hedge funds, other alternative investments and illiquid investments); Working with the lead Investment Team member to conduct in-depth due diligence on external fund managers/investment products; Conduct continuous monitoring of existing investments/external fund managers. Maintain risk sheets, databases and other monitoring tools; Update, aggregate and prepare data and reports, as needed (more...)
